@TOKEN = {{ login.response.body.token }}

### GET ALL USERS
GET http://localhost:5000/api/users HTTP/1.1

### GET A USER ? public
GET http://localhost:5000/api/users/1 HTTP/1.1

### ADD A USER ? public
POST http://localhost:5000/api/users/new HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
  "title": "New post title",
  "body": "New post body"
}

### UPDATE A USER ? public
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/users/edit/2 HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated title",
  "body": "Updated body"
}

### DELETE A USER ? public
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/users/3 HTTP/1.1


