### endpoint - Cadastro de banco ###
### GET ALL BANKS
GET http://localhost:5000/api/banks HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}


### GET A BANK ? public
GET http://localhost:5000/api/banks/3 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### ADD A BANK ? public
POST http://localhost:5000/api/banks/new HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
  "code": 240,
  "description": "value_1983",
  "status": 1
}

### UPDATE A BANK ? public
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/banks/edit/2 HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
  "code": 240,
  "description": "value_2023",
  "status": 0
}

### DELETE A BANK ? public
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/banks/2 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

